Simon's struggling campaign have narrowed the Democratic race to
three men _ Gore, Massachusetts Gov. Michael Dukakis and Jesse
Jackson.
   ``Out of the three remaining candidates, Sen. Gore is the
candidate most attuned to our concerns in the South and Southwest.
