president plans to make. It said he will nominate Simeon Timothy
Lake III, 43, of Houston, Tex., as a U.S. district judge for the
southern district of Texas and Karl S. Forester, 47, of Harlan,
Ky., as a U.S. district judge for the Eastern District of Kentucky.
