she will run New York City's Plaza Hotel, which her husband
recently purchased for $390 million.
   Mrs. Tolley didn't say whether she would give Mrs. Trump tips on
how to negotiate a salary. At the time of the Plaza purchase, Trump
announced his wife would work for $1 and all the dresses she can
