   The Make A Wish Foundation learned she wanted to meet the
illusionists, and arranged the visit Tuesday night after their show.
   Roy told Cassandra to ``hang in there and be tough.''
   Her problems began with a strep throat infection that traveled
to her kidney when she was 2. Doctors later discovered her liver
was too swollen to permit a kidney transplant, and suspected her
heart was also diseased.
