<TEXT>
   Jesse Jackson is running for president on a
liberal platform he calls ``the opposite of Reaganomics'' _ raising
taxes on the rich, slashing Pentagon spending, creating a national
health program for all, doubling the budget for education and
raising the minimum wage.
   Jackson, who has finished first or second in most of the
